{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>Badges</h1>\n<h2>Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\">  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>c-badge c-badge--dark<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Dark Badge<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Demo</h2>\n<p><span class=\"c-badge c-badge--dark\">Dark Badge</span>\n<br>\n<br>\n<span class=\"c-badge c-badge--dark u-font--semibold\">Dark Badge (Semibold)</span>\n<br>\n<br>\n<span class=\"c-badge c-badge--dark u-bg-red\">Dark Badge (Red BG)</span>\n<br>\n<br>\n<span class=\"c-badge c-badge--outline-light\">Outline Light Badge</span>\n<br>\n<br></p>\n<h3>Using dark background to illustrate the light colors</h3>\n<div class=\"u-window-padding--2x u-bg-blue-dense-2 u-color-ink-opacity-4\">\n<span class=\"u-font--xsmall\">\n</span>\n<br>\n<br>\n<span class=\"c-badge c-badge--light\">Light Badge</span>\n<br>\n<br>\n<span class=\"c-badge c-badge--light u-font--semibold\">Light Badge (Semibold)</span>\n<br>\n<br>\n<span class=\"c-badge c-badge--outline-dark\">Outline Dark Badge</span>\n<br>\n<br>\n<span class=\"c-badge c-badge--outline-dark u-bg-red\">Outline Dark Badge (Red BG)</span>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Badges"}}},"pageContext":{"pathSlug":"/docs/badges"}}